    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Al-le--lu--i--a, al-le--lu---i----a, al-------le--lu----i----a. \n\nBend Thy bow, and pro-ceed pros-per-ous-ly, and be king, be-cause of truth and meek-ness__ and right---eous----ness. \n\nAl-le--lu--i--a, al-le--lu---i----a, al-------le--lu----i----a. \n\nThou hast loved right-eous-ness and hat-ed in-iq-ui-ty. Where-fore God, Thy God, hath a-noint-ed Thee with the oil of glad-ness more than__ Thy__ fel---lows.__\n\nAl-le--lu--i--a, al-le--lu---i----a, al-------le--lu----i-----a.________"
    }
  }
